behavior fill_dishwasher_with_dish_soap(dish_soap: item, dishwasher: item):

behavior __goal__():

        # Select dish soap
        bind dishwasher: item where:

behavior __goal__():

Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Add dish soap to the dishwasher.', '2. Load the bowls and plates into the dishwasher.', '3. Use
 the dishwasher to wash the bowls and plates.']

behavior add_soap_to_dishwasher(soap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        assert is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Ensure that the item is indeed a dishwasher
        assert is_soap(soap)
        # Ensure that the item is dish soap
        achieve inside(soap, dishwasher)
        # Place dish soap inside the dishwasher

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher in the scene
        
        bind dish_soap: item where:
            is_soap(dish_soap)
        # Select dish soap in the scene

        add_soap_to_dishwasher(dish_soap, dishwasher)

Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Put dish soap in the dishwasher.', '2. Wash the bowls and plates using the dishwasher.']

behavior put_dish_soap_in_dishwasher(dish_soap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(dish_soap, dishwasher)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        bind dish_soap: item where:
            is_soap(dish_soap)
            # Assuming dish_soap is a type of soap
        put_dish_soap_in_dishwasher(dish_soap, dishwasher)
